@startuml
title Watchdog - System Context

skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Monospaced
skinparam ArrowColor #2d2d2d

actor "Operators\n(DevOps/SRE)" as Ops
actor "Producers\n(Apps/Agents)" as Prod

rectangle "Watchdog Platform" as WD {
  rectangle "Watcher Service\n(ingest + normalize)" as Watcher
  rectangle "Core Service\n(tickets + rules)" as Core
  rectangle "NLP Service\n(enrichment)" as NLP
  rectangle "Dashboard\n(roadmap)" as UI
}

database "PostgreSQL\n(core store)" as PG
queue "Message Broker\n(optional)" as Broker
cloud "Log Store\n(optional)" as LogStore

Prod --> Watcher : send logs/metrics
Watcher --> Core : forward events\n(gRPC or broker)
Core --> NLP : analyze text\n(gRPC sync or async)
Core --> PG : persist tickets

Ops --> UI : view tickets\nconfigure rules
UI --> Core : management APIs

Watcher ..> Broker : publish events\n(optional)
Core ..> Broker : consume events\n(optional)
NLP ..> Broker : consume/publish\n(optional)

Watcher ..> LogStore : write raw logs\n(optional)
NLP ..> LogStore : fetch raw logs\n(optional)

@enduml
